ex21: Cockpit

Willem A. (Vlakkies) Schreuder
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2023


Demonstrates how to draw a cockpit view for a 3D scene.


Key bindings
  m          Toggle cockpit mode
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
